Class Labels

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.data.Labels

  • public final class Labels
extends Object
    Contains the labels of the chart.
    Is able to manage also multi-line labels.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
